<h4><span id="Personnalit.C3.A9"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Personnalité">Personnalité</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Samuel_Beckett&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=12" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Personnalité">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Samuel_Beckett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Modifier la section : Personnalité">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h4>
